<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>스쿱 - 관심있는 동호회를 찾아보세요</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/main/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pretendard:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
</head>
<body>
  
  <div id="loading">
    <img src="/public/images/logo.png" alt="스쿱" id="club_logo" />
  
    <div class="loader">
      <div class="loading-text">
        스쿱에 오신것을 환영합니다
        <span class="dot">.</span>
        <span class="dot">.</span>
        <span class="dot">.</span>
      </div>
  
      <div class="loading-bar-background">
        <div class="loading-bar">
          <div class="white-bars-container">
            <div class="white-bar"></div>
            <div class="white-bar"></div>
            <div class="white-bar"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("../common/header", {data}) %>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="map-container">
      <div id="map">
        <div class="zoom-level-label" id="zoomLabel">지역단위</div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="map-right-content">
        <div class="map_category_bar">
          <button class="category-btn active">회원순</button>
          <button class="category-btn">좋아요순</button>
          <button class="category-btn">조회순</button>
          <button class="category-btn">평점순</button>
        </div>
  
        <div class="club-list">
          <div class="initial-message" style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; color: #777;">
            <p>지도에서 지역을 선택하거나 카테고리 버튼을 클릭하여 동호회를 찾아보세요.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include("../common/side_bar") %>
  <%- include("../common/footer") %>

  <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=b809f71776d66974e4cb1caee3375cea"></script>
  <script src="/public/script/main/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>